 I'm sending this to you, because I think it has the best chance of being read here =)<P>

 [flattery]<P>

 I'm an avid Evercrack fan and have been for almost 8 months now.  Through these 8 months, there has not been a single second where I've felt like I was satisfied.  There is always something to do, somewhere to go,
