 What I guess I'm trying to say here, is that the EQ team has created a
world that hundreds of thousands of people find facinating.  How is a thing like this done without a dedicated and talented design team?  Well, it's not.<P>

 The EQ team has my utmost respect.  The models are fantastic (for the
amount of polys available to use), outdoor areas are stunning, indoor areas are breathtaking, classes are balanced, races are unique, tech support is available, and cheaters are dealt with.  Some people regret sending 10
bucks a month to a company that wastes their time.  Sure, it wastes my time, but in the most incredibly amazing and exilarating way I know of.<P>

 [/flattery]<P>

