models' movement are based on a bones system... are all races the same set of
bones, stretched and contorted to fit the model?  Or do they differ?<P>

 The models are excellent, considering the technological barriers you had
to work within.  Also, thank whoever did the skins, because they did an excellent job as well =)<P>

